To Run This Project
Step 1: Download & Extract

cd ~/ros2_ws/src
unzip isaac_sim_nav2.zip

Step 2: Run with the Interactive Script

cd ~/ros2_ws
./src/isaac_sim_nav2/run_project.sh

This gives you a menu to:
Build the project
Run Nav2 + RViz
Run with multi-goal navigator
Record/replay test sessions

Or Use Direct Commands

# Full setup and run
./src/isaac_sim_nav2/run_project.sh full

# Just run navigation
./src/isaac_sim_nav2/run_project.sh run

# Run with waypoint navigation
./src/isaac_sim_nav2/run_project.sh navigate
Prerequisites on Your Machine
Before running, make sure:
Isaac Sim is running with ROS2 bridge enabled
Your robot has LiDAR & odometry publishing to /scan, /odom, /tf
ROS2 Humble is installed
Quick Verification

# Check if Isaac Sim is connected
ros2 topic list | grep scan
# Should show: /scan
